==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Arabin
<hw>Ar"a*bin</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A carbohydrate, isomeric with cane sugar,
contained in gum <xex>arabic</xex>, from which it is extracted as a
white, amorphous substance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Mucilage, especially that made of gum
arabic.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Arabinose</ent>⟦br⟧
